OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChurch reverses decision   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnot to hire female vicars  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Cornwall church council's decision to
OL,6, ban women from applying to be the new  
OL,7, vicar has been reversed after a new    
OL,8, governing body was appointed.          
OL,10,FFowey Parochial Church Council (PCC)   
OL,11,Fpassed a resolution in March to        
OL,12,Fadvertise for a male priest-in-charge  
OL,13,Fat Fowey Parish Church St Fimbarrus.   
OL,15,FBut local residents criticised the move
OL,16,Fas sexist and "profoundly wrong".      
OL,18,FAs a result, Cornwall church council   
OL,19,Fchairman Andy Virr and two other PCC   
OL,20,Fmembers stood down.                    
